cars.postBody: This 2012 Subaru Impreza is in wonderful condition, has custom leather seats and white pearl paint job with a sport premium Trim. For those who don't know, the Impreza is excellent on gas mileage and has wonderful life span as well as generally easy up keep. The car has AUX/USB hookups for music and phone built in, features a Bluetooth phone connection option, and has a great sound system (nothing custom). On top of that the car is AWD, so driving in the snow is a blast! This car is still mostly owned by the bank, so selling would go down with or at a financial institution. It's really quite easy if you're willing to take a loan, but we can go over details of course. Shoot me an email and I would be happy to chat with you! P.S. I'm willing to negotiate on the price but not by much. It's a solid car with a whole life ahead of it. No interior damage. So if you're seriously interested in purchasing it we will be heading to the bank to handle the lien and get the title. Just wanted to put that out there upfront.
